Subject: RE: [T2] Spray in p/u truck bedliner for floors

  5 years ago I helped a friend get his 21 window bus back on the road. We
replaced the rockers, outriggers and belly pans. After all was done we
undercoated the whole underside with 2 part bed liner (150.00 dollars for a
4 litre kit) He lives at the beach and surfs all the time, which puts the
bus at the beach constantley. To this day the underside of his bus is still
perfect. A very worthwhile expenditure. 

ronnie

