Chris,

As I have explained to you in prior messages all my vehcles have
urethane balck bed liner on the bottom surfaces of them.
My 85 GL has had it on there for at least 4 years--has seen and
apprciated copious amounts of calcium chloride spray and is as good as
when I put it on ---

